      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Democrats from the country want\na man elected to the legislature who\nwill introduce a new road law. The\nfarmers are kicking on the road work\nbeing done and claim it's poor quality\nis due to the general nature Of the old\nlaw. They want a new law which\nspecifically requires certain things.\nThe Deep Creek road and its treat\nment this year is an especial matter\nof complaint. The farmers say less\nroad work has been done this year\nthan for several years."
